{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"A fact"},{"time":2000,"text":"came out of MIT,"},{"time":5000,"text":"couple of years ago. Ken Hale,"},{"time":7000,"text":"who's a linguist,"},{"time":9000,"text":"said that of the 6,000 languages"},{"time":12000,"text":"spoken on Earth right now,"},{"time":14000,"text":"3,000 aren't spoken by the children."},{"time":17000,"text":"So that in one generation,"},{"time":20000,"text":"we're going to halve our cultural diversity."},{"time":24000,"text":"He went on to say"},{"time":26000,"text":"that every two weeks,"},{"time":28000,"text":"an elder goes to the grave"},{"time":30000,"text":"carrying the last spoken word"},{"time":32000,"text":"of that culture."},{"time":34000,"text":"So an entire philosophy,"},{"time":39000,"text":"a body of knowledge about the natural world"},{"time":41000,"text":"that had been empirically gleaned over centuries,"},{"time":45000,"text":"goes away."},{"time":47000,"text":"And this happens every two weeks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":51000,"text":"So for the last 20 years,"},{"time":53000,"text":"since my dental experience,"},{"time":56000,"text":"I have been traveling the world"},{"time":59000,"text":"and coming back"},{"time":61000,"text":"with stories about some of these people."},{"time":63000,"text":"What I'd like to do right now"},{"time":65000,"text":"is share some of those stories with you."},{"time":68000,"text":"This is Tamdin."},{"time":70000,"text":"She is a 69-year-old nun."},{"time":74000,"text":"She was thrown in prison in Tibet for two years"},{"time":77000,"text":"for putting up a little tiny placard"},{"time":79000,"text":"protesting the occupation of her country."},{"time":83000,"text":"And when I met her, she had just"},{"time":86000,"text":"taken a walk over the Himalayas"},{"time":88000,"text":"from Lhasa, the capital of Tibet,"},{"time":91000,"text":"into Nepal, across to India --"},{"time":93000,"text":"30 days --"},{"time":95000,"text":"to meet her leader, the Dalai Lama."},{"time":98000,"text":"The Dalai Lama lives in Dharamsala, India."},{"time":100000,"text":"So I took this picture three days"},{"time":102000,"text":"after she arrived,"},{"time":104000,"text":"and she had this beat-up pair of tennis shoes on,"},{"time":106000,"text":"with her toes sticking out."},{"time":108000,"text":"And she crossed in March,"},{"time":110000,"text":"and there's a lot of snow at 18,500 feet in March."}]},{"cues":[{"time":115000,"text":"This is Paldin."},{"time":117000,"text":"Paldin is a 62-year-old monk."},{"time":119000,"text":"And he spent 33 years in prison."},{"time":123000,"text":"His whole monastery was thrown into prison"},{"time":126000,"text":"at the time of the uprising,"},{"time":129000,"text":"when the Dalai Lama had to leave"},{"time":132000,"text":"Tibet."},{"time":134000,"text":"And"},{"time":136000,"text":"he was beaten, starved,"},{"time":139000,"text":"tortured -- lost all his teeth while in prison."},{"time":141000,"text":"And when I met him, he was a kind gentle old man."},{"time":145000,"text":"And it really impressed me --"},{"time":147000,"text":"I met him two weeks after he got out of prison --"},{"time":150000,"text":"that he went through that experience, and ended up"},{"time":152000,"text":"with the demeanor that he had."}]},{"cues":[{"time":155000,"text":"So I was in Dharamsala meeting these people,"},{"time":158000,"text":"and I'd spent about five weeks there,"},{"time":161000,"text":"and I was hearing these similar stories"},{"time":163000,"text":"of these refugees that had poured out of Tibet"},{"time":166000,"text":"into Dharamsala."},{"time":168000,"text":"And it just so happened, on the fifth week,"},{"time":171000,"text":"there was a public teaching by the Dalai Lama."},{"time":175000,"text":"And"},{"time":177000,"text":"I was watching this crowd of monks and nuns,"},{"time":180000,"text":"many of which I had just interviewed,"},{"time":182000,"text":"and heard their stories,"},{"time":184000,"text":"and I watched their faces,"},{"time":187000,"text":"and they gave us a little FM radio,"},{"time":189000,"text":"and we could listen to the translation of his teachings."},{"time":192000,"text":"And what he said was:"},{"time":194000,"text":"treat your enemies as if they were precious jewels,"},{"time":198000,"text":"because it's your enemies"},{"time":200000,"text":"that build your tolerance and patience"},{"time":203000,"text":"on the road to your enlightenment."},{"time":207000,"text":"That hit me so hard,"},{"time":211000,"text":"telling these people that had been through this experience."}]},{"cues":[{"time":215000,"text":"So, two months later, I went into"},{"time":218000,"text":"Tibet, and I started"},{"time":220000,"text":"interviewing the people there, taking my photographs. That's what I do."},{"time":223000,"text":"I interview and do portraits."},{"time":226000,"text":"And this is a little girl."},{"time":228000,"text":"I took her portrait up on top of the Jokhang Temple."},{"time":231000,"text":"And I'd snuck in --"},{"time":233000,"text":"because it's totally illegal to have a picture of the Dalai Lama in Tibet --"},{"time":238000,"text":"it's the quickest way you can get arrested."},{"time":241000,"text":"So I snuck in a bunch of little wallet-sized pictures of the Dalai Lama,"},{"time":244000,"text":"and I would hand them out."},{"time":246000,"text":"And when I gave them to the people,"},{"time":249000,"text":"they'd either hold them to their heart,"},{"time":251000,"text":"or they'd hold them up to their head and just stay there."},{"time":254000,"text":"And this is --"},{"time":256000,"text":"well, at the time -- I did this 10 years ago --"},{"time":258000,"text":"that was 36 years after the Dalai Lama had left."}]},{"cues":[{"time":263000,"text":"So"},{"time":264000,"text":"I was going in, interviewing these people and doing their portraits."},{"time":268000,"text":"This is Jigme and her sister, Sonam."},{"time":270000,"text":"And they live up on the Chang Tang, the Tibetan Plateau,"},{"time":273000,"text":"way in the western part of the country."},{"time":276000,"text":"This is at 17,000 feet."},{"time":278000,"text":"And they had just come down from the high pastures,"},{"time":281000,"text":"at 18,000 feet."},{"time":283000,"text":"Same thing: gave her a picture,"},{"time":285000,"text":"she held it up to her forehead."},{"time":287000,"text":"And I usually hand out Polaroids"},{"time":290000,"text":"when I do these, because I'm setting up lights,"},{"time":292000,"text":"and checking my lights,"},{"time":294000,"text":"and when I showed her her Polaroid, she screamed and ran into her tent."}]},{"cues":[{"time":299000,"text":"This is Tenzin Gyatso;"},{"time":301000,"text":"he was found to be the Buddha of Compassion at the age of two,"},{"time":305000,"text":"out in a peasant's house,"},{"time":308000,"text":"way out in the middle of nowhere."},{"time":310000,"text":"At the age of four, he was installed"},{"time":312000,"text":"as the 14th Dalai Lama."},{"time":315000,"text":"As a teenager, he faced"},{"time":317000,"text":"the invasion of his country,"},{"time":319000,"text":"and had to deal with it -- he was the leader of the country."},{"time":322000,"text":"Eight years later, when they discovered there was a plot"},{"time":324000,"text":"to kill him,"},{"time":326000,"text":"they dressed him up like a beggar"},{"time":328000,"text":"and snuck him out of the country on horseback,"},{"time":331000,"text":"and took the same trip that Tamdin did."},{"time":334000,"text":"And he's never been back to his country since."},{"time":338000,"text":"And"},{"time":340000,"text":"if you think about this man,"},{"time":342000,"text":"46 years later,"},{"time":344000,"text":"still sticking"},{"time":346000,"text":"to this non-violent response"},{"time":350000,"text":"to a severe political and human rights issue."},{"time":354000,"text":"And the young people,"},{"time":356000,"text":"young Tibetans, are starting to say, listen, this doesn't work."},{"time":359000,"text":"You know, violence as a political tool"},{"time":361000,"text":"is all the rage right now."},{"time":363000,"text":"And"},{"time":366000,"text":"he still is holding this line."},{"time":368000,"text":"So this is our icon"},{"time":370000,"text":"to non-violence in our world --"},{"time":373000,"text":"one of our living icons."}]},{"cues":[{"time":376000,"text":"This is another leader of his people."},{"time":378000,"text":"This is Moi. This is in the Ecuadorian Amazon."},{"time":381000,"text":"And Moi is 35 years old."},{"time":384000,"text":"And"},{"time":386000,"text":"this area of the Ecuadorian Amazon --"},{"time":388000,"text":"oil was discovered in 1972."},{"time":391000,"text":"And in this period of time -- since that time --"},{"time":394000,"text":"as much oil, or twice as much oil"},{"time":397000,"text":"as was spilled in the Exxon Valdez accident,"},{"time":400000,"text":"was spilled in this little area of the Amazon,"},{"time":403000,"text":"and the tribes in this area have constantly had to move."},{"time":407000,"text":"And Moi"},{"time":409000,"text":"belongs to the Huaorani tribe,"},{"time":411000,"text":"and they're known as"},{"time":413000,"text":"very fierce, they're known as \"auca.\""},{"time":415000,"text":"And they've managed to keep out"},{"time":418000,"text":"the seismologists and the oil workers"},{"time":420000,"text":"with spears and blowguns."},{"time":423000,"text":"And we spent --"},{"time":425000,"text":"I was with a team --"},{"time":428000,"text":"two weeks with these guys out in the jungle"},{"time":431000,"text":"watching them hunt."},{"time":433000,"text":"This was on a monkey hunt,"},{"time":435000,"text":"hunting with curare-tipped darts."},{"time":438000,"text":"And the knowledge that these people have"},{"time":441000,"text":"about the natural environment is incredible."},{"time":443000,"text":"They could hear things, smell things, see things I couldn't see."},{"time":447000,"text":"And I couldn't even see the monkeys"},{"time":449000,"text":"that they were"},{"time":451000,"text":"getting with these darts."}]},{"cues":[{"time":455000,"text":"This is Yadira,"},{"time":457000,"text":"and Yadira is"},{"time":459000,"text":"five years old. She's in a"},{"time":462000,"text":"tribe that's neighboring the Huaorani."},{"time":465000,"text":"And her tribe has had to move"},{"time":467000,"text":"three times in the last 10 years because of the oil spills."},{"time":471000,"text":"And we never hear about that. And the latest"},{"time":474000,"text":"infraction against these people is,"},{"time":477000,"text":"as part of Plan Colombia,"},{"time":479000,"text":"we're spraying Paraquat or Round Up, whatever it is --"},{"time":482000,"text":"we're defoliating thousands of acres"},{"time":485000,"text":"of the Ecuadorian Amazon"},{"time":487000,"text":"in our war on drugs."},{"time":489000,"text":"And these people are the people who take the brunt of it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":493000,"text":"This is Mengatoue."},{"time":495000,"text":"He's the shaman of the Huaorani,"},{"time":497000,"text":"and"},{"time":500000,"text":"he said to us, you know, I'm an older man now;"},{"time":503000,"text":"I'm getting tired, you know; I'm tired"},{"time":505000,"text":"of spearing these oil workers."},{"time":507000,"text":"I wish they would just go away."},{"time":512000,"text":"And I was -- I usually travel alone"},{"time":515000,"text":"when I do my work, but I did this --"},{"time":518000,"text":"I hosted a program for Discovery,"},{"time":520000,"text":"and when I went down with the team,"},{"time":523000,"text":"I was quite concerned about"},{"time":526000,"text":"going in with a whole bunch of people, especially into the Huaorani,"},{"time":529000,"text":"deep into the Huaorani tribe."},{"time":531000,"text":"And"},{"time":533000,"text":"as it turned out, these guys really"},{"time":535000,"text":"taught me a thing or two about blending in"},{"time":538000,"text":"with the locals."},{"time":540000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":543000,"text":"One of the things I did"},{"time":546000,"text":"just before 9/11 --"},{"time":549000,"text":"August of 2001 --"},{"time":551000,"text":"I took my son, Dax,"},{"time":553000,"text":"who was 16 at the time,"},{"time":556000,"text":"and I took him to Pakistan."},{"time":558000,"text":"Because at first I wanted --"},{"time":560000,"text":"you know, I've taken him on a couple of trips,"},{"time":562000,"text":"but I wanted him to see"},{"time":564000,"text":"people that live on a dollar a day or less."},{"time":567000,"text":"I wanted him to get an experience"},{"time":569000,"text":"in the Islamic world"},{"time":571000,"text":"and I also wanted him to --"},{"time":574000,"text":"I was going there to work with a group,"},{"time":576000,"text":"do a story on a group called the Kalash,"},{"time":578000,"text":"that are a group of animists, 3,000 animists,"},{"time":580000,"text":"that live -- very small area --"},{"time":584000,"text":"surrounded by Islam -- there's 3,000"},{"time":587000,"text":"of these Kalash left; they're incredible people."},{"time":591000,"text":"So it was a great experience for him. He stayed up all night with them,"},{"time":594000,"text":"drumming and dancing."},{"time":596000,"text":"And he brought a soccer ball,"},{"time":598000,"text":"and we had soccer every night in this little village."}]},{"cues":[{"time":601000,"text":"And then we went up"},{"time":603000,"text":"and met their shaman."},{"time":605000,"text":"By the way, Mengatoue was the shaman"},{"time":607000,"text":"of his tribe as well."},{"time":609000,"text":"And this is John Doolikahn,"},{"time":611000,"text":"who's the shaman of the Kalash."},{"time":614000,"text":"And he's up in the mountains,"},{"time":616000,"text":"right on the border with Afghanistan."},{"time":618000,"text":"In fact, on that other side is the area, Tora Bora,"},{"time":621000,"text":"the area where"},{"time":624000,"text":"Osama bin Laden's supposed to be. This is the tribal area."},{"time":627000,"text":"And we watched"},{"time":630000,"text":"and stayed with"},{"time":632000,"text":"John Doolikahn."},{"time":634000,"text":"And the shaman -- I did a whole series on shamanism,"},{"time":637000,"text":"which is"},{"time":639000,"text":"an interesting phenomenon."},{"time":641000,"text":"But around the world,"},{"time":643000,"text":"they go into trance in different ways,"},{"time":645000,"text":"and in Pakistan,"},{"time":647000,"text":"the way they do it is they burn juniper leaves"},{"time":650000,"text":"and they sacrifice an animal,"},{"time":653000,"text":"pour the blood of the animal on the leaves"},{"time":655000,"text":"and then inhale the smoke."},{"time":657000,"text":"And they're all praying"},{"time":660000,"text":"to the mountain gods"},{"time":663000,"text":"as they go into trance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":667000,"text":"You know,"},{"time":669000,"text":"getting kids used to different realities,"},{"time":673000,"text":"I think, is so important. What Dan Dennett said the other day --"},{"time":677000,"text":"having a curriculum where they study different religions,"},{"time":680000,"text":"just to make a mental flexibility,"},{"time":682000,"text":"give them a mental flexibility"},{"time":684000,"text":"in different belief systems --"},{"time":686000,"text":"I think this is so necessary in our world today"},{"time":689000,"text":"as you see these clash of beliefs taking place."},{"time":693000,"text":"And all the security issues they cause us."},{"time":697000,"text":"So, one thing we did five years ago:"},{"time":700000,"text":"we started a program that links kids"},{"time":703000,"text":"in indigenous communities with kids in the United States."},{"time":705000,"text":"So we first hooked up"},{"time":708000,"text":"a spot in the Navajo Nation with a classroom in Seattle."},{"time":713000,"text":"We now have 15 sites."},{"time":716000,"text":"We have one in Kathmandu, Nepal;"},{"time":719000,"text":"Dharamsala, India; Takaungu, Kenya --"},{"time":721000,"text":"Takaungu is one-third Christian, one-third Muslim"},{"time":724000,"text":"and one-third animist, the community is --"},{"time":727000,"text":"Ollantaytambo, Peru,"},{"time":729000,"text":"and Arctic Village, Alaska."}]},{"cues":[{"time":731000,"text":"This is Daniel; he's one of our students"},{"time":733000,"text":"in Arctic Village, Alaska."},{"time":735000,"text":"He lives in this log cabin --"},{"time":737000,"text":"no running water, no heat other than --"},{"time":740000,"text":"no windows"},{"time":742000,"text":"and high-speed Internet connection."},{"time":744000,"text":"And this is --"},{"time":746000,"text":"I see this rolling out all over --"},{"time":748000,"text":"this is our site in Ollantaytambo, Peru, four years ago,"},{"time":751000,"text":"where they first saw their first computers;"},{"time":753000,"text":"now they have computers in their classrooms."},{"time":756000,"text":"And the way we've done this --"},{"time":758000,"text":"we teach digital storytelling to these kids."},{"time":761000,"text":"And we have them tell stories about issues in their community"},{"time":764000,"text":"in their community that they care about."},{"time":766000,"text":"And this is in Peru, where the kids told the story"},{"time":768000,"text":"about a river that they cleaned up."},{"time":770000,"text":"And the way we do it is, we do it in workshops,"},{"time":773000,"text":"and we bring people who want to learn"},{"time":776000,"text":"digital workflow and storytelling,"},{"time":780000,"text":"and have them"},{"time":782000,"text":"work with the kids."},{"time":784000,"text":"And just this last year we've taken a group of teenagers in,"},{"time":788000,"text":"and this has worked the best."},{"time":790000,"text":"So our dream is to bring teenagers together,"},{"time":792000,"text":"so they'll have a community service experience"},{"time":795000,"text":"as well as a cross-cultural experience,"},{"time":798000,"text":"as they teach kids in these areas"},{"time":800000,"text":"and help them build their communication infrastructure."}]},{"cues":[{"time":803000,"text":"This is teaching Photoshop"},{"time":806000,"text":"in the Tibetan children's village in Dharamsala."},{"time":810000,"text":"We have the website, where the kids all get their homepage."},{"time":813000,"text":"This is all their movies. We've got about 60 movies"},{"time":815000,"text":"that these kids have made,"},{"time":817000,"text":"and they're quite incredible."},{"time":819000,"text":"The one I want to show you --"},{"time":821000,"text":"after we get them to make the movies,"},{"time":824000,"text":"we have a night where we show the movies to the community."},{"time":827000,"text":"And this is in Takaungu --"},{"time":829000,"text":"we've got a generator and a digital projector,"},{"time":831000,"text":"and we're projecting it up against a barn,"},{"time":833000,"text":"and showing one of the movies that they made."},{"time":836000,"text":"And if you get a chance, you can go to our website, and you'll see"},{"time":839000,"text":"the incredible work these kids do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":842000,"text":"The other thing:"},{"time":845000,"text":"I wanted to give indigenous people a voice."},{"time":847000,"text":"That was one of the big motivating factors."},{"time":850000,"text":"But the other motivating factor is"},{"time":852000,"text":"the insular nature of our country."},{"time":855000,"text":"National Geographic just did a Roper Study"},{"time":858000,"text":"of 18 to 26 year olds"},{"time":861000,"text":"in our country"},{"time":863000,"text":"and in nine other industrialized countries."},{"time":866000,"text":"It was a two million dollar study."},{"time":868000,"text":"United States came in second to last"},{"time":871000,"text":"in geographic knowledge."},{"time":873000,"text":"70 percent of the kids couldn't find"},{"time":875000,"text":"Afghanistan or Iraq on a map;"},{"time":878000,"text":"60 percent couldn't find India;"},{"time":881000,"text":"30 percent couldn't find the Pacific Ocean."},{"time":884000,"text":"And this is a study"},{"time":886000,"text":"that was just done a couple of years ago."}]},{"cues":[{"time":890000,"text":"So what I'd like to show you now,"},{"time":893000,"text":"in the couple of minutes I have left,"},{"time":895000,"text":"is a film that a student made in Guatemala."},{"time":897000,"text":"We just had a workshop in Guatemala."},{"time":900000,"text":"A week before we got to the workshop,"},{"time":903000,"text":"a massive landslide, caused by Hurricane Stan,"},{"time":907000,"text":"last October, came in and buried"},{"time":909000,"text":"600 people alive in their village."},{"time":911000,"text":"And this kid lived in the village --"},{"time":913000,"text":"he wasn't there at the time --"},{"time":915000,"text":"and this is the little movie he put together about that."},{"time":919000,"text":"And he hadn't seen a computer before"},{"time":921000,"text":"we did this movie. We taught him Photoshop and --"},{"time":925000,"text":"yeah, we can play it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":950000,"text":"This is an old Mayan funeral chant"},{"time":953000,"text":"that he got from his grandfather."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1093000,"text":"Thank you very much."},{"time":1095000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}